entries.journal_entry_description: Help with the aftermath of the terrorist attack.
entries.journal_entry_title: Help with the Aftermath of the Terrorist Attack
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Even in the aftermath of the terrorist attack on Theed, many terrorists remain in the part of the city that suffered the attack. Help remove them from the city.
entries.task00_journal_entry_title: Help Remove the Terrorists from Theed
entries.task01_comm_message_text: We've received word that the terrorists have placed some bombs through the section of Theed that they attacked. Find and disarm the bombs.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: The terrorists left bombs in the attack zone. Find the bombs and disarm them.
entries.task03_comm_message_text: We need to restock the medical droids with supplies. Go to the hospital, get more supplies, and bring them to the medical droid throughout the attack zone.
entries.task04_journal_entry_description: Go gather medical supplies for the medical droids to use on victims of the terrorist attack. You'll find crates of supplies prepared and ready outside of the hospital.
entries.task05_journal_entry_description: Medical droids stand ready to aid anyone hurt in the terrorist attack zone. Bring the supplies you gathered to those droids.
entries.task05_journal_entry_title: Bring the Medical Supplies to the Medical Droids
entries.task05_retrieve_menu_text: Give the Droid some Medical Supplies
entries.task06_journal_entry_description: Report back to Major Franchels for further instructions.
